{"tid":689337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"登珠峰遇暴風雪奇蹟生還 美國女登山家跌落樓梯死","createTime":"2018-06-04T03:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T04:09:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22beb8f21fb9e02285121a8add36e1acfe48925f","tid":689337,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】美國61歲女登山家福克斯，曾於1996年在珠穆朗瑪峰遭遇死劫但奇蹟生還，惟近日卻在家中從樓梯上摔倒死亡。<br />\n<br />\n福克斯是美國首位攀登3座高達8000米高山的女性，同時亦是1996年珠穆朗瑪峰事故的生還者之一。當時她與其他登山人士一行10人，在珠穆朗瑪峰遇到強烈暴風雪，事件最終造成8人死亡，其後更被拍成電影《Everest》(《珠峰浩劫》)。<br />\n<br />\n福克斯生前接受訪問時表示，曾以為自己沒辦法活著回來，「暴雪非常痛苦，我覺得自己再也不能忍受，我只能蜷縮起來，希望死亡趕快降臨。」但她最終仍奇蹟生還。<br />\n<br />\n至上月24日，福克斯被好友發現從位於科羅拉多州的住家中從樓梯上摔倒死亡。福克斯在一生中歷經多次悲痛，她戀愛多年的男友1993年遇上雪崩不幸遇難，而她的丈夫馬丁亦在2004年因為滑翔意外離世。<br />\n<br />\n其好友表示，「看見她的遺體是很令人震驚與感到艱難的事情。」福克斯意外離世前曾向好友說過，很高興自己即將滿61歲，但沒想到之後卻天人永隔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Jp9VzIC2Y6f22za22WOTnA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-06-04/5fe80480-6791-11e8-ba84-a92cf7194e26_fall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJp9VzIC2Y6f22za22WOTnA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-06-04%2F5fe80480-6791-11e8-ba84-a92cf7194e26_fall.jpg&h=fac6548c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BB%E7%8F%A0%E5%B3%B0%E9%81%87%E6%9A%B4%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%AA%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E7%99%BB%E5%B1%B1%E5%AE%B6%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E6%AD%BB-143100596.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%258F%25A0%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259B%25AA%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B9%259F%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2582%2584-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E6%25AD%25BB-143100596.html&d=xViEvuVumwDc6BNzy5dOx3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=ca2e7a8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BB%E7%8F%A0%E5%B3%B0%E9%81%87%E6%9A%B4%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%AA%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%82%84-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E7%99%BB%E5%B1%B1%E5%AE%B6%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E6%AD%BB-143100596.html</a>"},{"pid":"369003462de5f50d35715dc5b6ac5d0856280bf3","tid":689337,"uid":2901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"ffdb5db1a9950f653c9477dee43725577a3590a0","tid":689337,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"死神來臨遲到了"}]}